{"tid":1692990,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「忽發其想」如果我嘅血液會傳染病，比狗打到流晒血，有冇機會傳比佢？","createTime":"2019-11-04T11:00:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T12:16:51.000Z","uid":232333,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"afb193cd59ce5fdc1b4b8526d45efc7be998d7a7","tid":1692990,"uid":232333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:00:28.000Z","msg":"首先聲明，我無意冒犯愛滋病或任何病患者，<br />\n如果真係令你唔舒服，我願意跪地道歉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我諗左好耐出唔出post，因為係一件悲劇。<br />\n<br />\n我日日睇住好多手足比狗打到頭破血流，突然諗過如果手足大嗌「我有愛滋病」，甚至向狗噴血。<br />\n<br />\n究竟會點？隻狗會唔會驚到縮？從而手足有機會走得甩？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據我所知，愛滋病可以透過血液傳染，而且需要一定量嘅dosage，所以平時生活上唔會傳染。<br />\n<br />\n但去到流晒血嘅地步又會唔會呢？特別係果陣隻狗好大機會有傷口。<br />\n<br />\n就算手足冇病，但咁樣嗌，會唔會令狗驚呢？<br />\n而且唔係驚一陣，係驚幾年。<br />\n如果真係有病，又真係傳染到隻狗，就......<br />\n<br />\n不過，愛滋病患者咁樣流血會唔會對自身特別危險我就唔清楚。(求FC)<br />\n<br />\n如果真係冒犯到手足，再次跪地道歉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對唔住！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a7aff5f4cd0f73114c8e46a6265579ff6469e17","tid":1692990,"uid":232333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3341086c9d51d2c988e794ee8fcfa8663071bb","tid":1692990,"uid":232333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:01:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"472584c48de9f6094fc9ef0e7e4f63c3e822c6eb","tid":1692990,"uid":232333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25160672e4662014fccd7c161fbb34c3f81b4245","tid":1692990,"uid":232333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:01:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f87082000009fd6fc28981c2ad6f74eda9e6bb9e","tid":1692990,"uid":232333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:02:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee689a6a1816916de70a51745fea824453b816f","tid":1692990,"uid":118827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:03:25.000Z","msg":"推<br />\naids透過血液傳播,咁掂到傷口你話傳唔傳到<br />\n最陰濕係班狗on duty咁耐,傷左邊度都唔知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe6db1e59c8f858b821b9ffcc13fb80d0991c5a","tid":1692990,"uid":18110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a568a78a3081e0bd6540be6527da03f9d43a36","tid":1692990,"uid":235665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:03:55.000Z","msg":"接觸到空氣好快死，要體液交流先得喎。"},{"pid":"bfaf4b6a28a13e73de5648c6375e23924defe720","tid":1692990,"uid":227166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:04:32.000Z","msg":"如果佢有傷口接觸到啲血就會，不過依家佢哋包實晒。。除非血入咗口/眼啦"},{"pid":"4bd42f78656555f6db64d57ff9a3bafdfa5bcc63","tid":1692990,"uid":267172,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:04:33.000Z","msg":"我諗你會害到FA手足先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5304f1ceded880343ec7243f407fe32fb0c03b76","tid":1692990,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec69d9ddad56a6a7467689053dd0913bc1a26421","tid":1692990,"uid":94828,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:05:11.000Z","msg":"傻啦 有乜性病啲狗冇架"},{"pid":"98115111b7bc57877c55426e29f7ad822510beec","tid":1692990,"uid":325884,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:08:14.000Z","msg":"如果你真係帶菌者，唔使諗住俾黑狗打到噴血，俾佢地拉返去雞姦就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f3d230f58c32fc38867d4ed2bcef33b6cadeb03","tid":1692990,"uid":40521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:08:34.000Z","msg":"盡量將d血揈去佢隻眼度<br />\n你頭流血 你就不停揈頭 盡量將啲血周圍飛<br />\n當然 要小心唔好整到手足"},{"pid":"5948ceeb7e384eee6c37464543afd803ce851994","tid":1692990,"uid":293816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:08:44.000Z","msg":"地底泥Popo表示 <br />\n咁啱嘅 我都有愛滋喎"},{"pid":"cf209e138f68e24c0f7a299fbf8420b0b2e17e0c","tid":1692990,"uid":306521,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:09:02.000Z","msg":"其他病唔知，但如果HIV positive又生勾勾出得嚟嘅都應該係食緊藥控制緊病情。依家啲藥已經可以將病毒控制到check唔到，亦唔會傳染，其本上同普通人無異。姐係如果傳染得嘅一係唔知自己有病/冇食藥，但唔食藥病情會惡化得好快，亦會有生命危險。再者現場會有其他手足，極易TK，所以可行性係零<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過啲狗會唔會咁有常識就第二件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4bd4f32f7b897b9bfdc44fdbfb6d218ae47d8b3","tid":1692990,"uid":144522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec69d9ddad56a6a7467689053dd0913bc1a26421","tid":1692990,"uid":94828,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:05:11.000Z","msg":"傻啦 有乜性病啲狗冇架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:09:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4db47036da2ad52c3b47615f9559bcb65df26ad0","tid":1692990,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:09:36.000Z","msg":"都唔屌你亂講aids呢樣 講野前用下腦先啦 係邊撚個會做急救呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d40d7b75646ddb7cebdee0962b8a7dd60330f16","tid":1692990,"uid":282289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:12:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw, 唔好insult patients, please."},{"pid":"999bf64a1eb0af0cd958d74272369b2f1e4a6399","tid":1692990,"uid":277572,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:19:19.000Z","msg":"對家一直吹緊風話有「天使」為「義士」提供性服務<br />\n<br />\n你拎愛滋病黎玩，一方面，對方可能真係信而驚左，但另一方面，對方又有題材做新聞，而且個可信性高左，因為真係有個人嗌出黎<br />\n<br />\n係得定失自己衡量一下"},{"pid":"340ed489090bb30e59c6b460ee04f99a0c51d1fc","tid":1692990,"uid":232333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4db47036da2ad52c3b47615f9559bcb65df26ad0","tid":1692990,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:09:36.000Z","msg":"都唔屌你亂講aids呢樣 講野前用下腦先啦 係邊撚個會做急救呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:19:21.000Z","msg":"真心對唔住<br />\n<br />\n但好奇想問，如果愛滋病患者有事，係會急救唔到？"},{"pid":"482271b0dba82dfab35e8a2db9b026d6cdffdb7f","tid":1692990,"uid":232333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:22:23.000Z","msg":"我唔係攞愛滋病來玩<br />\n<br />\n或者我表達得差，我都係諗下可唔可以嚇到班狗<br />\n<br />\n再次講對唔住🙏🏻"},{"pid":"c4d942486cf020180817dc1023df17080741043b","tid":1692990,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:25:12.000Z","msg":"會"},{"pid":"94959c13d2acdbf9e229f5709b103f424bbf19c6","tid":1692990,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98115111b7bc57877c55426e29f7ad822510beec","tid":1692990,"uid":325884,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:08:14.000Z","msg":"如果你真係帶菌者，唔使諗住俾黑狗打到噴血，俾佢地拉返去雞姦就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:33:58.000Z","msg":"唔知好嬲定好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}